- New features

-- Added Radar funcionality with multiple layers (Radar (Free, Provider by RainViewer API); Rain, Clouds, Temperature, Wind, Pressure (OWM key required))
-- Added an option to turn off the radar (General settings) with additional information
-- Added "Simple mode" for the widget popup with many customization settings
-- Added date and time in the widget header (optional)
-- Added date and time item information in the widget, tooltip and panel
-- Added a simple calendar when the date/time widget item is expandend
-- Added "Strip" layout in Forecast
-- Added dual temperature (C/F) support for panel, tooltip and widget (optional) in the Misc settings

- Improvements

-- Increase forecast days up to 16 (Open-Meteo)
-- Added an option to remove the "Today" forecast 
-- Removed "Location information" due to duplication with saved location 
-- Increased hourly forecast performance 
-- Remove auto scroll based on your current time in the "Today forecast". Now the past times are removed.

- Bug fixes
-- Fixed a bug where saved locations manually don't have any information about attitude and timezone.
-- Fixed a bug where the multi-location button was visible when one location is saved in the widget.